QuestData.Title: Just a Fancy Cockroach
QuestData.Description: Evidently, the ancient statues were home to various species of scarab.$b$bDetermined to leave this site in the best condition possible, you resolve to ridding the chamber of these pests.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Amethyst Scarabs, 5 Sapphire Scarabs, 5 Turquoise Scarabs, and 5 Emerald Scarabs.
QuestData.RewardText: As you obliterated the final scarab, you noticed an ancient piece of ornamental jewelry on the ground...
